---
import Site from "~/layouts/Site.astro";
// SSR (not prerender) so the corrections email comes from runtime env.
// CDN caches the rendered page; see Cache-Control below.
// EDIT-ME: editorial-standards copy is template default. Customize section
// bodies to match your own selection / AI-usage policy.
export const prerender = false;
const correctionsEmail = Astro.locals.runtime?.env?.CORRECTIONS_EMAIL
  ?? Astro.locals.runtime?.env?.CONTACT_EMAIL
  ?? "";
Astro.response.headers.set(
  "Cache-Control",
  "public, max-age=300, s-maxage=86400, stale-while-revalidate=86400",
);
---
<Site
  title="编辑标准 · Editorial standards — Glean · 拾遗"
  description="What 'every link human-reviewed' actually involves."
>
  <section class="page-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="lang-zh">编辑标准</span><span class="lang-en">Editorial standards</span></span>
      <h1 style="margin-top: 12px"><span class="lang-zh">“人审”的具体含义</span><span class="lang-en">What “human review” means</span></h1>
      <p><span class="lang-zh">“每条人审” 到底在审什么 · AI 能改什么 · 什么不能。</span><span class="lang-en">What “every link human-reviewed” actually involves · what AI may touch · what it can’t.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section--tight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="standards-prose prose-block">
        <h2><span class="lang-zh">1 · 什么会被选上</span><span class="lang-en">1 · What gets in</span></h2>
        <div class="yn-table">
          <div class="yn-yes">
            <h4><span class="lang-zh">✓ 进</span><span class="lang-en">✓ Accepts</span></h4>
            <ul>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">有<strong>新论点</strong>或<strong>新数据</strong>的工程内容</span><span class="lang-en">Engineering content with a <strong>new claim</strong> or <strong>new data</strong></span></li>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">作者是<strong>第一手</strong>实施者</span><span class="lang-en">Author is the <strong>first-hand</strong> implementer</span></li>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">官方 changelog / 设计文档 / RFC</span><span class="lang-en">Official changelogs / design docs / RFCs</span></li>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">深度复盘文章 / 工程事故 postmortem</span><span class="lang-en">Postmortems &amp; retrospective deep-dives</span></li>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">非英文一手内容 (中 / 日 / 德 …)</span><span class="lang-en">First-hand non-English sources (CN / JP / DE …)</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="yn-no">
            <h4><span class="lang-zh">✗ 拒</span><span class="lang-en">✗ Rejects</span></h4>
            <ul>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">Listicle “10 best …”</span><span class="lang-en">Listicles (“10 best …”)</span></li>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">Medium 转发文 / 内容农场</span><span class="lang-en">Medium re-blogs / content farms</span></li>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">“AI 替你总结了…” 的 AI 摘要文</span><span class="lang-en">AI-summarized AI-summary posts</span></li>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">付费墙后 80% 的文章</span><span class="lang-en">Articles 80% behind a paywall</span></li>
              <li><span class="lang-zh">明显的 affiliate / SEO link farm</span><span class="lang-en">Obvious affiliate / SEO link farms</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2><span class="lang-zh">2 · AI 在我们流程里能做什么</span><span class="lang-en">2 · What AI is allowed to do</span></h2>
        <p><span class="lang-zh">DeepSeek 在我们流程里只做<strong>三件事</strong>：抓正文、双语翻译、起草要点。它<strong>不</strong>决定选稿，<strong>不</strong>写编辑点评，<strong>不</strong>排序周刊。它的草稿在编辑面板里全部是<em>可编辑的</em>，发布前会被人改一遍——平均 60% 的卡片会被改至少一处。</span><span class="lang-en">DeepSeek does exactly three things: extracts the body, translates both ways, drafts bullet points. It does <strong>not</strong> select picks, write editor’s notes, or order the weekly. Its drafts are all editable in our admin panel — on average 60% of cards get at least one human edit before publish.</span></p>

        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="principle__head">AI · YES</div>
            <h3 class="principle__title"><span class="lang-zh">起翻译草稿</span><span class="lang-en">Translation draft</span></h3>
            <p class="principle__body"><span class="lang-zh">英中互译的第一稿。编辑会校对术语和语气。</span><span class="lang-en">First-pass EN↔ZH. A human checks term &amp; tone.</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="principle__head">AI · NO</div>
            <h3 class="principle__title"><span class="lang-zh">编辑点评</span><span class="lang-en">Editor’s note</span></h3>
            <p class="principle__body"><span class="lang-zh">“为什么读这一条”始终由人写。AI 永远不替编辑表态。</span><span class="lang-en">“Why read this” is always human-written. AI never takes a stance for us.</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="principle__head">AI · NO</div>
            <h3 class="principle__title"><span class="lang-zh">选稿决策</span><span class="lang-en">Selection</span></h3>
            <p class="principle__body"><span class="lang-zh">AI 可以给候选打 importance/novelty 分供编辑参考，但<strong>最终选 / 拒由编辑按下按钮</strong>。</span><span class="lang-en">AI may score candidates as a reference. <strong>Pick / reject is always a human click.</strong></span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <div class="principle__head">AI · YES</div>
            <h3 class="principle__title"><span class="lang-zh">标签建议</span><span class="lang-en">Tag suggest</span></h3>
            <p class="principle__body"><span class="lang-zh">从现有 tag 表里选 1-3 个。编辑可全部替换。</span><span class="lang-en">Picks 1–3 from existing taxonomy. Editor may replace all.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2><span class="lang-zh">3 · 利益冲突</span><span class="lang-en">3 · Conflicts of interest</span></h2>
        <p><span class="lang-zh">如果编辑或贡献者跟某条新闻的作者 / 公司有<strong>雇佣 / 顾问 / 投资关系</strong>，会在那条卡片底部加一行 <em>编辑披露</em>。我们不收任何形式的“推广费”——如果有，会在 /about 公告。</span><span class="lang-en">If an editor or contributor has an <strong>employment / advisory / investment</strong> relationship with the author or company of a pick, the card carries an <em>editor’s disclosure</em> line at the bottom. We take zero paid promotion — and we’d announce it on /about if we ever did.</span></p>

        <h2><span class="lang-zh">4 · 纠错与下架</span><span class="lang-en">4 · Corrections &amp; takedowns</span></h2>
        <blockquote>
          {correctionsEmail ? (
            <>
              <span class="lang-zh">发现错误？发邮件到 {correctionsEmail}。<br />技术细节有误 24 小时内修订并在文末标注；事实性错误重发勘误。</span>
              <span class="lang-en">Spot something wrong? Email {correctionsEmail}.<br />Technical mis-statements fixed within 24h with a footnote; factual errors trigger a corrigendum.</span>
            </>
          ) : (
            <>
              <span class="lang-zh">发现错误？通过站点页脚的联系方式告知。技术细节有误 24 小时内修订并在文末标注；事实性错误重发勘误。</span>
              <span class="lang-en">Spot something wrong? Reach out via the site footer. Technical mis-statements fixed within 24h with a footnote; factual errors trigger a corrigendum.</span>
            </>
          )}
        </blockquote>

        <h2><span class="lang-zh">5 · 做不到的事</span><span class="lang-en">5 · What I won’t pretend to do</span></h2>
        <p><span class="lang-zh">这不是“全栈技术媒体”。覆盖<strong>系统 · 工具 · 设计</strong>三个领域；硬件 / 学术论文 / 创业新闻 不在范围内。</span><span class="lang-en">This isn’t full-stack tech media. Coverage: <strong>systems · tooling · design</strong>. Hardware, academic papers, startup news — out of scope.</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Site>
